---

Snorcal integrates with the following upstream projects. Their code is not
included in this repository; snorcal talks to them over HTTP (sidecar mode)
or invokes their binaries as subprocesses (local dev mode). Each project
retains its own license and copyright.

  bambuddy (maziggy/bambuddy)
    Slicer sidecar runtime exposing OrcaSlicer + BambuStudio over HTTP.
    Used as prebuilt container images:
      ghcr.io/maziggy/orca-slicer-api:latest
      ghcr.io/maziggy/bambu-studio-api:latest
    License: GNU Affero General Public License v3.0
    Source:   https://github.com/maziggy/bambuddy

  OrcaSlicer (SoftFever/OrcaSlicer)
    Slicer engine invoked via the sidecar or as a local binary.
    License: GNU Affero General Public License v3.0
    Source:   https://github.com/SoftFever/OrcaSlicer

  BambuStudio (bambulab/BambuStudio)
    Slicer engine invoked via the sidecar or as a local binary.
    License: GNU Affero General Public License v3.0
    Source:   https://github.com/bambulab/BambuStudio

  orca-slicer-api (AFKFelix/orca-slicer-api)
    Reference HTTP API design that informed snorcal's sidecar integration.
    License: GNU Affero General Public License v3.0
    Source:   https://github.com/AFKFelix/orca-slicer-api
